---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Own Your Income — The $97 Course by Jaymes Corey"
    description="Stop renting your time to someone else's dream. Own Your Income is the no-fluff $97 course that shows you how to build your first real income stream — no guru promises, no passive income myths, no waiting."
    canonicalUrl="https://jaymescorey.com/own-your-income"
    ogImage="https://jaymescorey.com/images/og-jaymes.jpg"
    ogImageAlt="Own Your Income — The $97 Course by Jaymes Corey"
    ogType="product"
>
    <Fragment slot="head">

        <!-- Course structured data (Google rich results eligible) -->
        <script type="application/ld+json">{`
        {
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "Course",
          "name": "Own Your Income",
          "description": "The no-fluff course that shows you how to build your first real income stream — without quitting your job, without a huge following, and without waiting for the perfect moment.",
          "url": "https://jaymescorey.com/own-your-income",
          "image": "https://jaymescorey.com/images/og-jaymes.jpg",
          "provider": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Jaymes Corey",
            "url": "https://jaymescorey.com",
            "sameAs": ["https://www.linkedin.com/in/jaymescorey"]
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Jaymes Corey",
            "url": "https://jaymescorey.com"
          },
          "educationalLevel": "Beginner",
          "courseMode": "Online",
          "teaches": [
            "How to build your first income stream",
            "How to create and price a digital offer",
            "How to get your first paying customer without a large audience",
            "How to build repeatable income systems",
            "How to stack multiple income streams as a one-person business"
          ],
          "about": {
            "@type": "Thing",
            "name": "Building a one-person income stream",
            "description": "How to own your income by building a real, independent income stream from scratch"
          },
          "hasCourseInstance": {
            "@type": "CourseInstance",
            "courseMode": "Online",
            "courseWorkload": "PT2H",
            "instructor": {
              "@type": "Person",
              "name": "Jaymes Corey",
              "url": "https://jaymescorey.com",
              "description": "Navy Vet, Dad of 3, and one-person business builder who has built service businesses from zero to profit across multiple states."
            },
            "offers": {
              "@type": "Offer",
              "price": "97",
              "priceCurrency": "USD",
              "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock",
              "url": "https://jaymescorey.com/own-your-income",
              "validFrom": "2026-04-07",
              "seller": {
                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Jaymes Corey"
              }
            }
          }
        }
        `}</script>

        <!-- BreadcrumbList structured data -->
        <script type="application/ld+json">{`
        {
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 1,
              "name": "Home",
              "item": "https://jaymescorey.com/"
            },
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 2,
              "name": "Own Your Income",
              "item": "https://jaymescorey.com/own-your-income"
            }
          ]
        }
        `}</script>

        <!-- FAQ structured data (Google FAQ rich results) -->
        <script type="application/ld+json">{`
        {
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "FAQPage",
          "mainEntity": [
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "Do I need a business idea before I start Own Your Income?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "No. Module 2 walks you through picking your income stream from scratch. If you already have an idea, we will sharpen it. If you do not, we will find one that fits your actual life."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "How long does it take to get through the Own Your Income course?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "Six modules. If you move, you can finish in a weekend. If you implement as you go, plan on two to four weeks. It is built for people with full lives, not people with infinite free time."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "Will Own Your Income work if I have a full-time job and limited time?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "Yes. This course is built for that situation specifically. You do not quit your job to start building. You build while you have the safety net, so that by the time you want to make a bigger move, you have already got something working."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "What if I have zero audience and zero following?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "Module 4 covers exactly this. You do not need an audience to own your income. You need one customer. The course covers how to get that first customer without social media follower counts, without paid ads, and without waiting years to build an audience first."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "What is the refund policy for Own Your Income?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "If you complete the course and do the work and it does not move you toward owning your income, reach out. The goal is not to keep $97 from someone who genuinely put in the effort."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "Why does Own Your Income cost $97?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "$97 is real money — enough that you will actually open it — but not so much that it becomes the excuse not to start. Free courses get ignored. $997 courses become a thing you have to wait until the finances are better for. $97 is the number that makes you move without making you wait."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
        `}</script>

    </Fragment>

    <Nav />

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- HERO -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-hero">
        <div class="oyi-hero-inner">
            <span class="oyi-eyebrow">// The $97 Course — Instant Access</span>
            <h1>
                Own Your<br>
                <span class="oyi-hero-outline">Income.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="oyi-hero-sub">
                You don't have an income problem. You have a permission problem. You're waiting for someone else to tell you it's okay to build something of your own — and that wait is costing you more than you know.
            </p>
            <p class="oyi-hero-sub oyi-hero-sub--bold">
                This course ends the wait.
            </p>
            <a href="#checkout" class="btn oyi-cta-btn">Get Instant Access — $97 &nbsp;→</a>
            <div class="oyi-hero-meta">
                <span class="oyi-meta-pill">✓ Instant Access</span>
                <span class="oyi-meta-pill">✓ Go At Your Own Pace</span>
                <span class="oyi-meta-pill">✓ No Fluff. No Guru. Real Moves.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- TICKER -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="oyi-ticker" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="oyi-ticker-track">
            <span>Own Your Income</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Stop Renting Your Time</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Build One Thing</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Your First Income Stream</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>No Guru. No Gimmicks.</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>$97 — Start Today</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Own Your Income</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Stop Renting Your Time</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Build One Thing</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>Your First Income Stream</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>No Guru. No Gimmicks.</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
            <span>$97 — Start Today</span>
            <span class="oyi-tick-sep">◆</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE LIE -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-section oyi-paper oyi-reveal">
        <div class="oyi-inner">
            <span class="section-label">01 // The Lie</span>
            <h2 class="oyi-section-h2">
                They Sold You<br>
                <span class="oyi-outline-ink">"Passive Income."</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="oyi-prose-cols">
                <div class="oyi-prose">
                    <p>You've heard it a thousand times. Build a course. Start a dropshipping store. Create content. Set up a funnel. Sleep while the money rolls in.</p>
                    <p>So you researched. You watched hours of YouTube. You bought a course from someone with a rented Lamborghini in the thumbnail. You signed up for the email list of a guru who charges $5,000 to tell you what you could've figured out for free.</p>
                    <p>And now you're here — still searching, still reading, still waiting for the idea that finally feels real enough to start.</p>
                    <div class="oyi-pull">
                        The passive income promise is designed to keep you consuming, not building.
                    </div>
                    <p>The people selling you "passive income" make their money by selling the <em>idea</em> of passive income. That's their income stream. And it's not passive for you — it's another thing you bought that's sitting unfinished in a browser tab.</p>
                    <p>Here's the truth nobody says out loud: owning your income is not passive. Not at first. It requires building something real, and it requires you to actually start.</p>
                    <p>That's what this course is about.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-aside-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <p class="oyi-aside-stat">87%</p>
                    <p class="oyi-aside-label">of people who buy online courses never finish them.</p>
                    <p class="oyi-aside-note">// This one is built to be finished. Six modules. One clear outcome. No fluff.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE COST OF WAITING -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-section oyi-dark oyi-reveal">
        <div class="oyi-inner">
            <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--yellow);">02 // The Real Cost</span>
            <h2 class="oyi-section-h2" style="color: var(--paper);">
                Another Year.<br>
                <span style="-webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--yellow); color: transparent;">Same Situation.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="oyi-section-lead" style="color: rgba(246,241,231,0.75);">
                Let's do the math on waiting.
            </p>
            <div class="oyi-cost-grid">
                <div class="oyi-cost-card">
                    <span class="oyi-cost-num">52</span>
                    <span class="oyi-cost-label">weeks you spend waiting for the right time</span>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-cost-card">
                    <span class="oyi-cost-num">$0</span>
                    <span class="oyi-cost-label">in income from streams you haven't built yet</span>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-cost-card">
                    <span class="oyi-cost-num">1</span>
                    <span class="oyi-cost-label">income source — your employer — who can cut it tomorrow</span>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-cost-card">
                    <span class="oyi-cost-num">0</span>
                    <span class="oyi-cost-label">income streams that built themselves while you waited</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="oyi-dark-prose">
                You're not waiting for the right idea. You have the idea. You're waiting for permission. You want someone to tell you that it's real enough, safe enough, ready enough to start.
            </p>
            <p class="oyi-dark-prose">
                I'm telling you now: it never feels ready. You build it ready. You own your income by moving, not by waiting.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- WHAT "OWN YOUR INCOME" ACTUALLY MEANS -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-section oyi-cream oyi-reveal">
        <div class="oyi-inner">
            <span class="section-label">03 // The Reframe</span>
            <h2 class="oyi-section-h2">
                What It Really<br>
                <span class="oyi-outline-ink">Means to Own Your Income.</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="oyi-reframe-grid">
                <div class="oyi-reframe-block">
                    <span class="oyi-reframe-x">×</span>
                    <h3>It Does Not Mean</h3>
                    <ul class="oyi-reframe-list oyi-reframe-list--no">
                        <li>Quitting your job tomorrow</li>
                        <li>Building a 7-figure business from scratch</li>
                        <li>Going viral or growing a massive audience</li>
                        <li>Having a perfect idea before you move</li>
                        <li>Knowing exactly how it ends before it starts</li>
                        <li>Replacing your income overnight</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-reframe-divider"></div>
                <div class="oyi-reframe-block">
                    <span class="oyi-reframe-check">→</span>
                    <h3>It Means</h3>
                    <ul class="oyi-reframe-list oyi-reframe-list--yes">
                        <li>Having at least one income stream you control</li>
                        <li>Building something real that earns without a boss attached</li>
                        <li>Knowing how to create income — not just how to earn it</li>
                        <li>Not being one bad performance review from crisis</li>
                        <li>Moving toward total presence with the people that matter</li>
                        <li>Starting ugly and making it real through action</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="oyi-reframe-bottom">
                <p>Owning your income isn't a destination. It's a decision — the decision to stop being dependent on a single source of money that someone else controls. This course teaches you how to make that decision real.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- WHO THIS IS FOR -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-section oyi-paper oyi-reveal">
        <div class="oyi-inner">
            <span class="section-label">04 // Who This Is For</span>
            <h2 class="oyi-section-h2">
                You've Been Here<br>
                <span class="oyi-outline-ink">Before.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="oyi-section-lead">If any of these sound familiar, you're in the right place.</p>
            <div class="oyi-persona-grid">
                <div class="oyi-persona-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <span class="oyi-persona-num">01</span>
                    <h3>The Frustrated Employee</h3>
                    <p>You're good at your job. Maybe really good. But you're working hard to build someone else's dream and somewhere deep down it's eating at you. You want something that's yours. You just don't know where to start.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-persona-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <span class="oyi-persona-num">02</span>
                    <h3>The Side Hustle Seeker</h3>
                    <p>You've tried a few things. Maybe Etsy, maybe freelancing, maybe dropshipping. Nothing stuck. You need a clear process — not another idea — so you can actually finish something and get paid for it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-persona-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <span class="oyi-persona-num">03</span>
                    <h3>The Passive Income Skeptic</h3>
                    <p>You've been burned by the gurus. The $2,000 courses that delivered generic advice. The "just start a podcast" crowd. You want someone who's actually done it — without the hype — to show you the real path.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-persona-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <span class="oyi-persona-num">04</span>
                    <h3>The Almost-Started</h3>
                    <p>You have the idea. You've had it for a while. You know what you want to build. You just haven't pulled the trigger yet. You need a structure that forces you to move and someone to hold the standard while you do.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-persona-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <span class="oyi-persona-num">05</span>
                    <h3>The Safety Net Builder</h3>
                    <p>You're not trying to blow up. You just want one income stream that you own — something between you and the worst-case scenario. A cushion. A backup. A start. That's all. That's the right reason to be here.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-persona-card oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <span class="oyi-persona-num">06</span>
                    <h3>The Present Parent</h3>
                    <p>You've done the math. The way you're working right now doesn't add up to the life you want to live with your kids. You need income that isn't chained to a desk, a commute, or someone else's schedule. Same.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE METHOD -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-section oyi-yellow oyi-reveal">
        <div class="oyi-inner">
            <span class="section-label">05 // The Approach</span>
            <h2 class="oyi-section-h2 oyi-h2-ink">
                Build Ugly.<br>Earn Real.
            </h2>
            <div class="oyi-method-grid">
                <div class="oyi-method-text">
                    <p class="oyi-method-p">This is not a theory course. There are no slides full of frameworks that sound smart but fall apart the second you try to apply them to your actual life.</p>
                    <p class="oyi-method-p">Every module in Own Your Income is built around one principle: <strong>the move is the method.</strong> You learn by doing. You build by shipping. You own your income by building something and putting it in front of a real person who can pay for it.</p>
                    <p class="oyi-method-p">That's it. That's the whole approach. Ugly action beats perfect inaction every single time.</p>
                    <p class="oyi-method-p">I've built service businesses from zero in three different states. I've launched experiments across dozens of domains. I homeschool my kids and run income streams in public so people can see exactly what works and what doesn't. Not hypothetically. Actually.</p>
                    <p class="oyi-method-p">This course is what I wish someone had handed me before I wasted years waiting for the right moment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="oyi-method-card">
                    <div class="tape"></div>
                    <p class="oyi-method-card-text">The move<br>is the<br>method.</p>
                    <span class="oyi-method-card-sub">// Everything else is just delay</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- WHAT'S INSIDE THE COURSE -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="oyi-section oyi-dark oyi-reveal">
        <div class="oyi-inner">
            <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--yellow);">06 // Inside the Course</span>
            <h2 class="oyi-section-h2" style="color: var(--paper);">
                Six Modules.<br>
                <span style="-webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--yellow); color: transparent;">One Outcome.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="oyi-section-lead" style="color: rgba(246,241,231,0.65);">
                Own Your Income is six focused modules. No bloat. No filler. Every lesson moves you closer to a real income stream that you own.
            </p>

            <div class="oyi-modules">

                <div class="oyi-module oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="oyi-module-num">01</div>
                    <div class="oyi-module-body">
                        <span class="oyi-module-label">The Mindset Reset</span>
                        <h3 class="oyi-module-title">Why "Passive Income" Is Keeping You Broke</h3>
                        <p class="oyi-module-desc">We burn the passive income fantasy down and replace it with something that actually works: the ownership model. You'll finish this module with a clear understanding of what owning your income requires, why it's possible for you specifically, and the single mental switch that separates people who build from people who browse.</p>
                        <ul class="oyi-module-bullets">
                            <li>The myth that keeps most people consuming instead of building</li>
                            <li>What "owning your income" actually demands of you</li>
                            <li>The permission problem — and how to kill it permanently</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="oyi-module oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="oyi-module-num">02</div>
                    <div class="oyi-module-body">
                        <span class="oyi-module-label">The One Thing Rule</span>
                        <h3 class="oyi-module-title">Stop Starting Everything. Pick One.</h3>
                        <p class="oyi-module-desc">The fastest way to own nothing is to try to build everything at once. This module gives you a clear framework for picking the one income stream that fits your skills, your life, and your actual schedule. We cover the four types of income streams that work for one-person builders — and how to choose yours without second-guessing it to death.</p>
                        <ul class="oyi-module-bullets">
                            <li>The four income stream types and which one fits you</li>
                            <li>How to stop chasing shiny objects and go deep on one thing</li>
                            <li>The "ugly filter" — your one-question test for any idea</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="oyi-module oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="oyi-module-num">03</div>
                    <div class="oyi-module-body">
                        <span class="oyi-module-label">Build Your First Offer</span>
                        <h3 class="oyi-module-title">What to Sell, How to Price It, and Why It Has to Be Real</h3>
                        <p class="oyi-module-desc">Most people spend months "building" something that nobody ever sees. This module breaks the cycle. You'll build your first offer using the Ugly Offer Method — minimum viable, maximum clarity — so you can put something in front of a real buyer before you feel ready. Because feeling ready is not a prerequisite for getting paid.</p>
                        <ul class="oyi-module-bullets">
                            <li>The Ugly Offer Method — build it fast, price it right, ship it today</li>
                            <li>Pricing psychology for first-time income builders</li>
                            <li>How to write an offer page that converts without a copywriting degree</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="oyi-module oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="oyi-module-num">04</div>
                    <div class="oyi-module-body">
                        <span class="oyi-module-label">Your First Customer</span>
                        <h3 class="oyi-module-title">How to Get Paid Without a Big Audience, Ads, or Years of Grinding</h3>
                        <p class="oyi-module-desc">You don't need 10,000 followers to own your income. You need one paying customer first — and then the second one becomes a system. This module covers the exact outreach, positioning, and conversation moves that get you to a first sale without spending money on ads or begging the algorithm for attention.</p>
                        <ul class="oyi-module-bullets">
                            <li>The warm market method — your fastest path to a first sale</li>
                            <li>How to position your offer so people self-select in</li>
                            <li>The exact message framework for getting your first yes</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="oyi-module oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="oyi-module-num">05</div>
                    <div class="oyi-module-body">
                        <span class="oyi-module-label">The System</span>
                        <h3 class="oyi-module-title">Make It Repeatable So It Doesn't Own You</h3>
                        <p class="oyi-module-desc">The goal isn't to own your income and then have it own your time instead. This module is about building the basic systems that make your income stream work without you having to manually push it every single day. Simple, ugly, functional systems. Not automation fantasies — real repeatable processes that let you earn without burning out.</p>
                        <ul class="oyi-module-bullets">
                            <li>The three systems every income stream needs to run without you</li>
                            <li>How to build a simple delivery process that scales</li>
                            <li>When to automate vs. when to keep it manual</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="oyi-module oyi-reveal">
                    <div class="oyi-module-num">06</div>
                    <div class="oyi-module-body">
                        <span class="oyi-module-label">Stack It</span>
                        <h3 class="oyi-module-title">What Happens After One Stream Is Working</h3>
                        <p class="oyi-module-desc">Once you own one income stream, the game changes. You're no longer guessing — you have proof that you can build something and get paid for it. This final module shows you how to layer a second stream without tanking the first one, how to recognize when you're ready to scale, and how to think about income as a compounding asset instead of a monthly scramble.</p>
                        <ul class="oyi-module-bullets">
                            <li>The stacking sequence — how to add streams without losing focus</li>
                            <li>Income compounding: how each stream makes the next one easier</li>
                            <li>Signs you're ready to go deeper vs. wider</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="oyi-bonus oyi-reveal">
